'''Timmy''' was Rachel's boyfriend in Junior High.

In "[[The One With Rachel's Other Sister]]", [[Amy Greene]] claimed that [[Rachel Greene|Rachel]] stole Timmy from her, only for Rachel to reply that Timmy was her boyfriend and that Amy made out with him. Amy replied "Oh, come on. That was 20 years ago. Get over it."
